I have successfully implemented US-003: Stripe Elements checkout flow with all acceptance criteria fulfilled!

## What was implemented:

✅ **Complete Stripe checkout system:**
- `POST /api/billing/create-checkout` - Creates Stripe checkout sessions
- `POST /api/billing/create-subscription` - Processes successful payments
- Checkout modal with Stripe CardElement integration
- Payment success page with confirmation flow
- Reusable checkout button component
- Full pricing page with billing toggle

✅ **Key features:**
- Customer creation/retrieval linked to user IDs
- Subscription storage in database with proper status tracking
- Payment error handling with user-friendly messages
- Responsive design matching app theme
- Team plan support with team name collection

✅ **Quality gates passed:**
- TypeScript compilation ✅
- ESLint for new code ✅

The implementation provides a complete, production-ready checkout flow that users can use to subscribe to Pro or Team plans directly within the app. The system properly integrates with Stripe's secure payment processing while maintaining the existing app's design patterns and user experience standards.
